UI.DiscoveryIntroUi.cbceb58c:
When ye opt in, other RavaSync users who have also opted in can see that ye're on RavaSync. In practice, that means:
• A little ♥ can appear on yer nameplate fer them (an' theirs fer ye).
• ye can right-click each other an' send Mate requests directly.

If ye keep this off, ye stay invisible t' discovery. nay hearts, nay extra right-click option, an' people will need yer UID t' Mate.

UI.SettingsUi.InfoNotif.Title: Info Notification Display
UI.SettingsUi.InfoNotif.Help:
Where ye "Info" notices show up.
"Nowhere" shows no Info notices
"Chat" prints Info notices in chat
"Toast" shows toast notices down in the bottom-right
"Both" shows chat and the toast notice
